# Keep the Docker build context small. The image installs deps from
# package-lock.json and builds from source, so vendored/build/test artifacts
# and local secrets must never enter the context.
#
# Do NOT ignore prisma/ — the schema + committed migrations
# (prisma/migrations/20260617111242_init) must ship so `prisma migrate deploy`
# can run in the container. Do NOT ignore prisma.config.ts — Prisma 7 reads
# DATABASE_URL and the migrations path from it.

node_modules
dist
coverage
.git
test
**/*.spec.ts
.env
.env.*
*.log
.eslintcache
